  "description": {
    "de": "Alle Experten behaupten, dass Dremoan essbar sei, aber so richtig probieren wollte noch niemand. Die Farbe lässt darauf schließen, Dremoan könne radioaktiv sein.",
    "en": "All the experts insist that Dremoan is in fact edible, but no one has really had the courage to try: its colour is about as appetising as your great-aunt's special Gobball tripe. Not very.",
    "es": "Todos los expertos mantienen que Dremoan es comestible, pero nadie ha intentado jamás darle un bocado, ya que su color hace pensar que es radioactivo.",
    "fr": "Tous les experts maintiennent que Dremoan est bel et bien comestible, mais personne n'a réellement osé y goûter ; sa couleur laissant davantage penser qu'il serait radioactif.",
    "id": "442163",
    "pt": "Todos os especialistas afirmam que o Dermoan é realmente comestível, mas ninguém nunca se atreveu a prová-lo, já que a sua cor leva a crer que ele pode ser radioativo."
  },
